JOHANNESBURG, October 9  – Mamelodi Sundowns will host Bloemfontein Celtic in the opening round of the Telkom Knockout. The draw was made in Johannesburg on Monday, and the dates for the fixtures will be announced at a later stage. In other high-profile fixtures, hosts Orlando Pirates will welcome Chippa United while Black Leopards will travel to take on Kaizer Chiefs. Telkom draw:
AmaZulu v Cape Town City
Mamelodi Sundowns v Bloemfontein Celtic
Polokwane City v SuperSport United
Free State Stars v Bidvest Wits
Orlando Pirates v Chippa United
Kaizer Chiefs v Black Leopards
Maritzburg United v Highlands Park
Baroka v Golden Arrows 